title: r/Entitledparents Insane Mother Robs an Ambulance!
description:
r/Entitledparents In today's story, an incredibly entitled woman screams at two paramedics because their parked ambulance in her way. Keep in mind that she can park someplace else, but she decides that she wants THIS parking space and is going to scream at the ambulance workers until they leave. When they refuse to listen to her, she goes into the back of the ambulance and steals supplies! The cops catch her red-handed.
